  "text": "The exclusive physical-chemical properties of noble metal NPs (NMNPS) gives them high multifunctionality [CITATION_1] . Noble metallic nanoparticles, such as AuNPs, AgNPs, PtNPs, offer high stability, easy chemical synthesis and tuneable surface functionalization [CITATION_2] .",
